   Provider Letters

   Welcome to the Community care Licensing Division's (CCLD) Provider
   Letter homepage! Currently the letters available on this page are only
   a small portion of those issued and distributed by CCLD. If you are
   unable to find the specific letter you are looking for among these
   documents, please check back often since we will regularly be adding
   new files to those already here.

   The following are links to documents online in Portable Document Format
   (PDF). If you have any problem reading these files, perhaps you do not
   have Adobe's free Acrobat Reader software. To download the free reader
   click below:

